name: Fractionsteiner T-Shirt
description:
It's here, Main Event Press's debut shirt design!

We openly admit we are massive fans of the Fractionsteiner, with his masterful way with numbers and he's brutal honesty about the desires of the female of the species. He looks out for his own, and now we're looking out for your with this limited edition shirt!

The numbers don't lie on this shirt. When you wear this shirt, you have the statistics on your side and have have a 141% (and 2/3rds) chance of winning at whatever you're doing. Whether it's working on your peaks at the gym, showing off to the freaks down at the club or just beating down on some fat asses, you've got it all in this shirt!
